## Kullanım (Türkçe) / Usage (English)

```python
import grikod2 # Restart Kernel veya/or Restart Kernel and Clear Outputs


# Run this cell (Shift+Enter): Input: 100
# Output example
# 000:000
# 001:001
# 010:011
# 011:010
# 100:110
# 101:111
# 110:101
# 111:100
```
```python
import grikod2
grikod2.__version__
```
